name: Losing My Mind by Sophia Wilson

metadata.name: Strong
metadata.description:
Losing My Mind is an extension of 5 specific emotions that I've felt in the past year - the good, the bad, and the crazy.  This project is not only about mental health awareness, but also about the Black feminine figure and increasing representation for kids who look like me. 

1/1 Color Darkroom Hand Print, 2021
